Package org.jdrupes.mdoclet

Class DocCommentTreeWrapper

java.lang.Object
com.sun.tools.javac.tree.DCTree
com.sun.tools.javac.tree.DCTree.DCDocComment
org.jdrupes.mdoclet.DocCommentTreeWrapper
All Implemented Interfaces:
DocCommentTree, DocTree
public class DocCommentTreeWrapper extends com.sun.tools.javac.tree.DCTree.DCDocComment implements DocCommentTree
Feeds the results of the methods through the TreeConverter where appropriate.

With JDK 11, DocCommentTreeWrapper only had to implement DocCommentTree. Starting with (at least) JDK 15, javadoc casts (without check) DocCommentTree instances to DCTree.DCDocComment when reporting errors e.g. about a missing link target. That’s the only reason why the wrapper extends DCTree.DCDocComment.
